msgctxt "an9.70:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.70:0.2"
msgid "7. Satipaṭṭhānavagga "
msgstr "7. Mindfulness Meditation "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.70:0.3"
msgid "70. Uddhambhāgiyasutta "
msgstr "70. Higher Fetters "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.460, sc1
msgctxt "an9.70:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, uddhambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are five higher fetters. "

msgctxt "an9.70:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an9.70:1.3"
msgid "Rūparāgo, arūparāgo, māno, uddhaccaṃ, avijjā—"
msgstr "Desire for rebirth in the realm of luminous form, desire for rebirth in the formless realm, conceit, restlessness, and ignorance. "

msgctxt "an9.70:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcuddhambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni. "
msgstr "These are the five higher fetters. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an9.70:2.1"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ uddhambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ pahānāya … pe … ime cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "To give up these five higher fetters you should develop the four kinds of mindfulness meditation. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.70:2.2"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

